# No .env values are required for local play, mocked evals, or the browser demo.
#
# Ambient Director inference uses the Codex CLI and local `codex login` auth.
# Do not add OpenAI, Anthropic, or gateway API keys for the current ambient path.
#
# To change the dev-server port, set PORT in the shell before running:
#   PORT=3002 pnpm run dev
